arts.ttl: France vs Azerbaijan Broadcast – Time and Channel to Watch the Match
arts.sum: The French national team faces Azerbaijan this Sunday at 8:45 p.m. CET It will be at the Parc des Princes, as part of the 2026 World Cup qualifiers. This match will involve two Paris Saint-Germain players, both French: Lucas Chevalier (23-year-old goalkeeper) and Lucas Hernandez (29-year-old defender).
